shankari shamkuru
raagam: sAvEri
15 maayamaaLava gowLa janya
Aa:S R1 M1 P D1 S 
Av: S N3 D1 P M1 G3 R1 S

taaLam: tisram
Composer: Shyaamaa Shaastree
Language:

pallavi

shankari shamkuru candramukhi akhilANDEshvari shAmbhavi sarasija bhava vanditE gauri amba
anupallavi

sankaTa hAriNi ripu vidAriNi kalyANi sadA nata phaladAyikE haranAyikE jagatjanani
caraNam 1 

jambupati vilAsini jagadavannOlAsini kambukandharE bhavAni kapAladhAriNi shUlini

caraNam 2 

angaja ripu tOSiNi akhila bhuvana pOSiNi mangaLa pradE mrDAni marALa sannibha gamani

caraNam 3 

shyAmakrSNa sOdari shyAmaLE shAtOdari sAmagAna lOlE bAlE sadArthi bhanjana shIlE
